</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns nehst
                            <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>erynn<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
                        habt <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gewonh<ex>eit</ex></expan> und alts
                        <expan>herkome<ex>n</ex>s</expan>, die uns auch wol
                                <expan>wissenliche<ex>n</ex></expan> sein, daz ewr
                                <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kawfflewt bey uns zu
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> zollfrey und
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kawfflewt bey ewch zu Ach
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>umb</expan> auch zollfrey sein und
                                <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>süll<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, darumb ewr <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
                        und kawfflewt <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat und
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kawfflewt <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<pb facs="#facs_88" id="43r"/>stat jerlich pflichtig sein <expan>zu
                            geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> i pfunt <expan>pfeff<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, i par
                                <expan>hentschuhe<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> weiszen stab, die
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> etliche <expan>v<ex>er</ex>gangne</expan>
                        jare von den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> niht geraicht
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan>
<expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>; darauf ir in
                            <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> begeret mit den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>zu bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz söliche ergangne recht
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> geraicht <expan>wurd<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        etc. als die <expan>eingesloss<ex>en</ex></expan>
